                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Implement and optimize review systems, Q&A sections, and user photos. Leverage UGC for fresh
                  content, long-tail keywords, and social proof that drives conversions.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Service Card 6 -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div
                  class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-2 text-gray-900">Conversion Rate Optimization</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  SEO-driven CRO to turn organic traffic into revenue. Optimize product descriptions, images,
                  trust signals, and CTAs for maximum conversion rates.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-display mb-6 text-gray-900">
            Our E-commerce SEO Process
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
            A proven methodology designed specifically for online stores and product catalogs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg"
              >
                1
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-2 text-gray-900">
                  E-commerce SEO Audit
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Comprehensive audit of your online store including technical issues, product page optimization,
                  category strategy, site architecture, and competitive analysis specific to e-commerce.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg"
              >
                2
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-2 text-gray-900">Keyword Research</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Product-specific keyword research identifying high-intent commercial keywords. Map keywords to
                  products and categories based on search volume, competition, and buyer intent.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg"
              >
                3
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-2 text-gray-900">Technical Implementation</h3>
